        <para id="id1169132417071">Now this conversion factor can be used to determine the number of liters of fuel that should have been transferred to the fuel tanks.</para>
        <equation id="id1169121011160">
          <m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
            <m:semantics>
